{"title" : "十八岁成人礼" ,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>一个人一生中，最难忘的是</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁那成长的瞬间！儿时的稚嫩在那一刻成熟起来，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体'>幼时的顽皮在那一刻变成了沉甸甸的责任！这就是</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体'>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁，不仅获得法律意义的成人标志，也是作为个体由青少年时期转入成人时期心灵成长的标志！</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'> 同时</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁，每一个家庭也希望能够让孩子懂得更多人生的道理！</SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>金牌拓展为达成广大家庭的需求，将成长教育融入十八岁成人礼，让孩子们在活动中，回顾自己的成长、父母的付出、社会的变化、未来的期望！让十八岁成人礼，成为</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>年生活的缩影，成为未来梦想的起点！</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>金牌拓展为“十八岁成人礼”精心设计两种形式：</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>形式一：中式“十八岁成人礼”</SPAN></B><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>以军营为活动场所，在传统的感言、誓词、寄语等环节外，我们精心设置了：</SPAN>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>年生活回顾，以纪录片方式播放</SPAN>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>年成长的每一个至关重要或难望的环节或事件，由父母亲自为孩子进行讲解。同进加入了孩子与家庭成员互动环节：如我为父母献支歌等。在对未来的畅想环节是，金牌设置了“</SPAN>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁梦想记录箱”，我们将为每一个家庭的孩子的</SPAN>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁梦想记录免费保存</SPAN>20<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>年，孩子成家立业或有了下一代后，可来金牌拓展取回，这也是金牌与</SPAN>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁孩子们的美好约定！</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>形式二：西式“十八岁成人礼”</SPAN></B><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>以星级酒店为活动场所，在中式成人礼所有环节的基础上，增加西式无酒精</SPAN>party<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>环节。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>在</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>party<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>环节，增加孩子与父母互动性节目，让孩子们的</SPAN>18<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁成人礼，在高雅、欢乐、和谐、感动的氛围中完成。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>每种成人礼后，金牌都为每个家庭准备了经过后期精心剪辑制作的活动光碟，作为回赠礼。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>报名参加办法：</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>以家庭为单位报名，满</SPAN>6<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>组家庭举办，提前一月报名。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>"}